{"tid":892090,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"約左港鐵asuna搵茅場晶彥，真係搵到","createTime":"2018-11-06T15:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T02:33:02.000Z","uid":14941,"like":9,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c01988ab73e945657379d594686b36006c774ef","tid":892090,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"約了港鐵asuna小姐去圖書館，希望在公共電腦內找到茅場晶彥的蹤影<br />\n<br />\n搵搵下突然有人攝入黎，霸左我地部電腦，佢係港鐵呀叔！<br />\n<br />\n當我一拍佢膊頭，佢就轉頭望住我講：「immortal object。」<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢就係茅場，今次被發現，要奬勵我地。<br />\n佢雙手撩左幾下，話：「打嬴我就俾你logout部電腦」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我答：「好！」<br />\n<br />\n之後下意識伸手向背後拔劍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7PtU5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7PtU5n.png&h=d62db790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接著asuna 小姐捉住我衫領帶左我返屋企了。"},{"pid":"ac1ec3f8ed9a16e5baf54d94c3ffa9347a237e43","tid":892090,"uid":35667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SO0MFcM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSO0MFcM.png&h=a4936948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ef156391b219dddee1784c022f992aef93aa3b","tid":892090,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"下姐係點=="},{"pid":"215717f14d011ffecfefa46cd58767a2250aff17","tid":892090,"uid":209097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"低質左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9b6ec46c96424627172160d0399afc7d8ff53f","tid":892090,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"高質<br />\n支持繼續"},{"pid":"ab5c74521fa9a2092fd6d2f6e7eceb41a2de49a2","tid":892090,"uid":2223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSp-f8IHRNgHq0O